title: Protests after Russia launches Syria campaign
text:
Campaigners gathered outside the Russian Embassy Credit: ITV News Protesters have gathered outside the Russian Embassy tonight following news that Russia launched bombing raids on Syria for the first time. Police were called when campaigners spilled into the road at Kensington Palace Gardens.
Campaigners gathered outside the Russian Embassy Credit: ITV News Last updated Wed 30 Sep 2015 World
